{
  "stem": "3994.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to do our duty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father said, where are the others?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't you do something?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they have been shooting quite a few.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was the situation that everybody wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Jewish community couldn't go together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't go even to the temple, because they didn't allow anything to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At home if we were game enough to light the candles or anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we never knew when [INAUDIBLE]-- when will come somebody and do something to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were no keeping Kosher, because you couldn't get anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That went on about for four months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in end of-- beginning of '44.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was I allowed to?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody went?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't stop me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we knew when we went, they do something to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was a old Rabbi, Rabbi [NON-ENGLISH] was his name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was living where the synagogue is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even him, they took him away quite a few times, and let him out, and put him-- put him back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So nobody wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody could go even if you wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
